   313→## Part 2: Frontend (share-ui)
   314→
   315→### 2.1 Add Trash Bin Tab to DocumentsView
   316→
   317→**File:** `src/components/documents/DocumentsView.tsx`
   318→
   319→Add new section and tab:
   320→
   321→```typescript
   322→import DeleteForeverIcon from '@mui/icons-material/DeleteForever';
   323→import RestoreIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Restore';
   324→
