## Part 3: Migration

For existing documents, you need to add `validFrom`/`validUntil` to their existing relationships. Run this Cypher migration:

```cypher
// Add validFrom/validUntil to existing BELONGS_TO relationships
MATCH (d:Document)-[r:BELONGS_TO]->(ctx)
WHERE r.validFrom IS NULL
SET r.validFrom = coalesce(d.createdAt, datetime()), r.validUntil = NULL

// Add validFrom/validUntil to existing SHARED_WITH relationships
MATCH (d:Document)-[r:SHARED_WITH]->(sh)
WHERE r.validFrom IS NULL
SET r.validFrom = coalesce(d.createdAt, datetime()), r.validUntil = NULL

// Add validFrom/validUntil to existing CONTRIBUTED_TO relationships
MATCH (d:Document)-[r:CONTRIBUTED_TO]->(rt)
WHERE r.validFrom IS NULL
SET r.validFrom = coalesce(d.createdAt, datetime()), r.validUntil = NULL
```

