## Testing Checklist

- [ ] Create document → should have `validFrom` set, `validUntil` = NULL
- [ ] Move to trash → `validUntil` should be set to current time
- [ ] Document should NOT appear in regular document lists
- [ ] Document should appear in Trash Bin
- [ ] Restore document → new `BELONGS_TO` with `validUntil` = NULL created
- [ ] Document should appear in regular document lists again
- [ ] Permanent delete → document completely removed from Neo4j
- [ ] S3 files deleted on permanent delete

